{
  "chapter": {
    "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24",
    "translationId": "lxxe",
    "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
    "chapterNumber": 24,
    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 24 in Brenton's English Septuagint."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.1",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:1",
      "text": "And they number the sons of Aaron in their division, Nadab, and Abiud, and Eleazar, and Ithamar.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.2",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:2",
      "text": "And Nadab and Abiud died before their father, and they had no sons: so Eleazar and Ithamar the sons of Aaron ministered as priests.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.3",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:3",
      "text": "And David distributed them, even Sadoc of the sons of Eleazar, and Achimelech of the sons of Ithamar, according to their numbering, according to their service, according to the houses of their fathers.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.4",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:4",
      "text": "And there were found among the sons of Eleazar more chiefs of the mighty ones, than of the sons of Ithamar: and he divided them, sixteen heads of families to the sons of Eleazar, eight according to their families to the sons of Ithamar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.5",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:5",
      "text": "And he divided them according to their lots, one with the other; for there were those who had charge of the holy things, and those who had charge of the house of the Lord among the sons of Eleazar, and among the sons of Ithamar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.6",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:6",
      "text": "And Samaias the son of Nathanael, the scribe, of the family of Levi, wrote them down before the king, and the princes, and Sadoc the priest, and Achimelech the son of Abiathar were present; and the heads of the families of the priests and the Levites, each of a household were assigned one to Eleazar, and one to Ithamar.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.7",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:7",
      "text": "And the first lot came out to Joarim, the second to Jedia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.8",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:8",
      "text": "the third to Charib, the fourth to Seorim,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.9",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:9",
      "text": "the fifth to Melchias, the sixth to Meiamin,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.10",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:10",
      "text": "the seventh to Cos, the eighth to Abia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.11",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:11",
      "text": "the ninth to Jesus, the tenth to Sechenias,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.12",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:12",
      "text": "the eleventh to Eliabi, the twelfth to Jacim,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.13",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:13",
      "text": "the thirteenth to Oppha, the fourteenth to Jesbaal,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.14",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:14",
      "text": "the fifteenth to Belga, the sixteenth to Emmer,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.15",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:15",
      "text": "the seventeenth to Chezin, the eighteenth to Aphese,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.16",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:16",
      "text": "the nineteenth to Phetaea, the twentieth to Ezekel,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.17",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:17",
      "text": "the twenty-first to Achim, the twenty-second to Gamul,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.18",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 18,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:18",
      "text": "the twenty-third to Adallai, the twenty-fourth to Maasai.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.19",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:19",
      "text": "This is their numbering according to their service to go into the house of the Lord, according to their appointment by the hand of Aaron their father, as the Lord God of Israel commanded.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.20",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 20,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:20",
      "text": "And for the sons of Levi that were left, even for the sons of Ambram, Sobael: for the sons of Sobael, Jedia.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.21",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 21,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:21",
      "text": "For Raabia, the chief was Isaari,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.22",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 22,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:22",
      "text": "and for Isaari, Salomoth: for the sons of Salomoth, Jath.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.23",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 23,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:23",
      "text": "The sons of Ecdiu; Amadia the second, Jaziel the third, Jecmoam the fourth.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.24",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 24,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:24",
      "text": "For the sons of Oziel, Micha: the sons of Micha; Samer.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.25",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 25,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:25",
      "text": "The brother of Micha; Isia, the son of Isia; Zacharia.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.26",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 26,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:26",
      "text": "The sons of Merari, Mooli, and Musi: the sons of Ozia,",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.27",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 27,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:27",
      "text": "That is, the sons of Merari by Ozia, —his sons were Isoam, and Sacchur, and Abai.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.28",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 28,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:28",
      "text": "To Mooli were born Eleazar, and Ithamar; and Eleazar died, and had no sons.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.29",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 29,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:29",
      "text": "For Kis; the sons of Kis; Jerameel.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.30",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 30,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:30",
      "text": "And the sons of Musi; Mooli, and Eder, and Jerimoth. These were the sons of the Levites according to the houses of their families.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "lxxe:first-chronicles.24.31",
      "translationId": "lxxe",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 24,
      "verseNumber": 31,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 24:31",
      "text": "And they also received lots as their brethren the sons of Aaron before the king; Sadoc also, and Achimelech, and the chiefs of the families of the priests and of the Levites, principal heads of families, even as their younger brethren.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    }
  ]
}
